Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:56.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(506,396)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.83,0:01:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王到处都是客人还有客人的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me restaurant is packed to the gills
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with customers and their money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.07,0:01:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  收银机又塞满了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, the register is full again
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来处理  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.97,0:01:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么没排队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you in line?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想吃蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.30,0:01:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实想吃  可走过去太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love one, but it's so far away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:38.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(492,670)}打包堡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口感没蟹黄堡好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not quite as good as a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我一英寸都用不着走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I didn't have to move one inch
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.73,0:01:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那餐车把我客人偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That food truck stole me customer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.27,0:01:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是客人不来蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if the customers won't come to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就把蟹堡王带给客人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bring the Krusty Krab to them
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我们到外面来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, what are we doing out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.22,0:02:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的大方老板有惊喜要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your generous employer has a surprise for you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱你的惊喜  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love your surprises, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最爱的惊喜就是橡皮支票了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My favorite surprise was the rubber check
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.69,0:02:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a good one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:17.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206,720)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的全新  至少我这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me brand new--to me--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐车  蟹堡巡游舰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,food truck, the Krusty Kruiser
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一堆垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a hunk of junk
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一辆大帅车才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More like a big hunk of gorgeous
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱可不开那破车卖蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We won't sell any patties from that old jalopy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.52,0:02:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我把蟹黄堡卖出去  否则不准回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better sell a patty or you better not come back
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.67,0:02:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来开车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're driving
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以导航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can navigate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.57,0:02:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Joy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,服务客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Customers, ho
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get going
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只缺靠近饿肚子顾客的车位了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all we need is a parking spot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,next to lots of hungry customers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个位子不错  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks like a good spot, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:11.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1118,786)}隔油池
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我位子  讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my spot, you creep
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try over there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,678)}蝌蚪卷饼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边找到了空位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found an empty spot in here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.20,0:03:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建筑工人一下子就会饿着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Construction workers are always hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买热乎乎的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your red-hot Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,870)}吊车煎饼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,占我摊位的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You claim jumpers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my turf
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon appétit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.19,0:04:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方挺有格调
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now this place looks classy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来买美味平价蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your delicious, affordable Krabby Patties here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平价
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Affordable?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平无奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How common
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法式开胃小菜车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Canapé truck
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:20.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,978)}上流法式开胃小菜
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.30,0:04:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都走遍全裤头村了  啥都卖不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We tried all over Bikini Bottom and didn't sell a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去跟蟹老板说我们失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go back and tell Krabs we failed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱还有一个地方没去试过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's one place we still haven't tried
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,592)}石头滩
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头滩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快转  快转
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn, turn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,800)}您正在驶出裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fn@Adobe 黑体 Std R\pos(1410.098,588.999)}石头滩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.032,355)}则所
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方也太荒凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is deserted
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没记错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1528,528)}唐果
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.02,0:05:03.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公交站那边会有石头滩的好心居民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there are always
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:03.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,friendly Rock Bottomites at the bus stop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1366,446)}公较
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.65,0:05:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想得可真美啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a fabulous idea, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里客人可真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are so many customers here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能都在石头滩商场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe the Rock Bottom mall?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,商场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mall
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fn@Adobe 黑体 Std R\pos(998.098,292.999)}石头滩商场
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去马戏团的应该比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The circus should be good for crowds
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怕是都去跳蚤马戏团了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a flea circus?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是温的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still warm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:39.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,362)}募地
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墓地也没人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cemetery is empty too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方连鬼城都算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place isn't even a ghost town
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  咱尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we tried
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A customer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来买好吃又稍微新鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step right up and get a delicious, half-fresh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,562)}凯皮吉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回一定要抓到他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got him this time
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟丢他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We lost him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we go home now?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说想要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs said we can't go back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少得卖出一个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until we sell at least one Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.80,0:07:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  那我就自己买蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll just buy a stupid patty myself
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.48,0:07:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我钱包忘在放家里的裤子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgot my wallet in my pants at home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.75,0:07:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob, could you please
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借我一点钱买个蟹黄堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lend me some money to buy a patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只带了蟹堡币
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only carry Krusty Kash
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在蟹堡王无效
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Not valid at the Krusty Krab"?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来要想回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess if I ever want to go home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.27,0:07:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只能把蟹黄堡卖给神秘怪人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we have to sell a patty to that mysterious weirdo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.57,0:07:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来用我的捉水母技能追踪他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll track him down using my jellyfishing expertise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:39.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(897.133,613)}公较总占
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got ya
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的脑干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My brainstem
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看丛林鱼漫画学到的这招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I learned this trick reading Jungle Fish Comics
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到那个小浑蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got the little barnacle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:24.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,318)}公较
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然都回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, since I'm never going home
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是在这舒服一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may as well get comfortable
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你们这群怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're those weirdos that have been
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,追着我到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chasing me around town
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你又干嘛朝我们招手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why were you waving at us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后又跑走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then running away?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不懂你的口音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't understand your accent
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来处理  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我石头滩话说得可流利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I speak fluid Rock Bottom-ish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.12,0:08:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.10,0:08:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Were you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朝我们招手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waving at us?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朝你们招手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waving at you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扇干我胳肢窝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drying out my armpits
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你卖个热乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sell you a hot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.47,0:09:04.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:04.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Delicious Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.61,0:09:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来还
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It does look
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tasty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡要卖出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna sell a patty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.86,0:09:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bert
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可惜你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad you couldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起每年例行去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come with us on our yearly trip to the
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过蟹黄堡还是给你买了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But here's your Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  弗兰克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Frank
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过要扇干胳肢窝真挺久的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you know how long these pits take to dry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两位抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然本来想向你们买蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to buy a patty from ya
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我手上已经有一整袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I already have a whole bag
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头滩居民好爱吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those Rock Bottomers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,really love their Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.72,0:10:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖了多少蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many patties did you sell?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,None
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.16,0:10:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们一整天都在搞什么名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of all that's greasy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have you been doing all day?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.42,0:10:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上回去  卖不出蟹黄堡不准回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going right back out there until you sell a patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点饿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a little hangry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经忙得都没空吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been so busy, I haven't eaten anything meself
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, fine
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正这钱还会归我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Comes straight back to me pocket anyhow
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算卖出一个蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We finally sold a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally go home
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.47,0:11:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花了钱  味道就跟蜗牛砂一个样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I have to pay for it, it tastes like old snail litter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.70,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,上流闺蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(695.802,342)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(709.802,636)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:34.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(707.802,572)}分镜指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(743.802,534)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(565.802,506)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.02,0:11:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the hold up in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现得跟没做过蟹黄堡似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:44.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're acting like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've never cooked a Krabby Patty before
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我本来就没做过蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's because I never have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cooked a Krabby Patty before
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要我做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you making me do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天是带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because today is bring--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.80,0:12:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  让女儿上班日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, put your daughter to work day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且海绵宝宝还在忙着清理木桶椅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, SpongeBob is busy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,deep cleaning the barrel chairs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.62,0:12:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你介不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not at all
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的餐到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your food or whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是不是你最棒的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just the best job ever?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你弟弟诺比在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's your brother, Nobby?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.27,0:12:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟诺比要去大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and Nobby was just on our way to the big city
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们就想接受你的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so we thought we'd take you up on your offer to
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你带我们观光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,show us the sights
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.15,0:12:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(776,622)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱们能跟我最爱的消防栓打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can say hi to my favorite fire hydrant
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能看喂蛤蜊的老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then we can see the old man that feeds the clams
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.07,0:12:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能抛弃那些可可爱爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't abandon these lovely people
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不就让我来带你们参观大城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then why don't I show you around the big city?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不稀罕别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care about these people
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小珍珍要带我们去冒险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little Pearly's gonna take us on an adventure?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dippity
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让我离开这就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything to get out of this place
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼愉快出游
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be a whale's day out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辛勤工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hard day's work
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺比说他要准备留下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobby says he's fixing to stay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮海绵宝宝给饿肚子客人做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and help SpongeBob with the hungry folk
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.70,0:13:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  看来咱们赚大发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Pearl, looks like we got ourselves a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会特别棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll be great
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.58,0:13:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两位鲸鱼姐妹一起探索大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two whale gals reconnoitering the big city together
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想一起去什么索大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we want to do that "noitering" thing in the city
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得提前预支一下我零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll need an advance on my allowance
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  这就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  拿木头会员卡才没法愉快出游
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:52.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad, we can't have a whale's day out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your balsa wood card
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1044,278)}鲤事达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,560)}尤金蟹先生
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要钻石不限量会员卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need the diamond unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024,372)}鲤事达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982,556)}尤金蟹先生
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My diamond
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没坐过潜水员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never took a Scuber before
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的太方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it sure is mighty convenient
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你载我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Preciate the lift
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大街上铺了口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These city streets is paved with chewing candy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你留着做纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm saving you as a souvenir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tasty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.89,0:14:32.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大城市里还有不少不恶心的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:32.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The city also has a lot of things in it that aren't gross
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说这些奢华小屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like these fancy shacks here?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  那是摩天大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, these are skyscrapers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1064,196)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是公交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's public transportation
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,道路施工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Street construction
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.72,0:15:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉就好像在穿越一部电视节目一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:15:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it's like walking through a TV show
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fries
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能够得到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I could reach them
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.02,0:15:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nobby
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是调料能再近点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now if only the condiments were closer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.75,0:15:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜面包架在厨房另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad the bun rack is on the other side of the room
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才叫快餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is what I call fast food
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是我最爱的百货店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite department store
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(818,368)}上流百货
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还是大城市的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, like, the heart of the big city
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上流百货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Upturn's
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这自动门太高档了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These here automatic doors sure is frilly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.05,0:16:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们山民做事更礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we hill folk do things a little more polite-like
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边请  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮人扶门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holding the door
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, you try
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳  那是上流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene, that's Lady Upturn
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.64,0:16:31.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:31.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她刚进城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's new in town
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会乖乖购物的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we'll be good shoppers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I swear
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.30,0:16:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去买吧  我的消费主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,carry on, my little consumerists
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.42,0:16:46.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但在上流百货这里购物一定要严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:46.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But here at Upturn's, we take shopping seriously
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,338)}上流香水
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临香水商店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the perfume department
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西死在里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think something done died up in here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死完上天堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Died and went to heaven
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,龙涎香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ambergris
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.39,0:17:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得清理一下你这边的过道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a cleanup on aisle you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不然再帮你试喷一点香水好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps another sample spritz?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.47,0:17:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我对那种恶臭不是很讲究
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I ain't too 'ticular about that stench
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我还有自己特色的臭气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, I carry my own signature stink
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毒蘑菇味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toadstool tang
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My nose
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horrible stench
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, we better cheese it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这件酷裙子好不好看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think about this cool dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:14.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1026,156)}更衣室
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kind of constricting
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请注意  上流百货的顾客们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Upturn's shoppers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞋店正在大促销
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a sale in the shoe department
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.97,0:18:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tenth floor
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,172)}上流电梯公司
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多鞋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So many shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No offense, Pearly girl
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的脚可穿不来鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but my feet don't cotton much to shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As the saying goes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.15,0:18:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大脚都有小鞋穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's a tiny shoe for every giant foot
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮你穿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合脚就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if the shoe fits
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你宰了我的细高跟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You slaughtered my stiletto
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.99,0:19:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早提醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认得你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you two
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就是刚刚那两个混混
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're those hooligans
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1362,330)}通缉
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狡诈鲸鱼来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's those wily whales
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红色警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Code red
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lady Upturn
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.03,0:19:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟娜琳只是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene and I were just having some fun
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,购物可不是来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shopping is not supposed to be fun
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.67,0:19:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好  我要禁止你们再来这里购物了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fortunately for me, you'll never be shopping here again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我有钻石不限量会员卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I had the diamond unlimited card
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056,336)}贵宾专用电梯
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两位小姐不属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, young ladies, do not belong here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤其是她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,especially her
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一我朋友就是不肯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what if my friend doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学着城里人的样子做事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do things the way city people do?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.00,0:20:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码她不会学你秀优越
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least she's not a stuck-up snob like you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.84,0:20:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们鲸鱼姐妹花一定要团结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We cetacean sisters always stick together
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钻石不限量卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Diamond unlimited
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.20,0:21:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bad
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王把你当马使唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like they worked you like a horse
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.25,0:21:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你陪我愉快出游  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the whale's day out, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.07,0:21:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过大城市实在太麻烦  不咋值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the big city's more trouble than it's worth
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.09,0:21:39.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后你就来乡下玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:39.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time, you're coming to the countryside
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  改天就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do that sometime
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.64,0:21:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  你上流百货消费怎么这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, what's the deal with all these charges at Upturn's?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.82,0:21:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还等什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why wait?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就去乡下玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the countryside right now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.64,0:22:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.05,0:22:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很快就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you real soon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会特别特别快的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sooner than you think
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.27,0:22:03.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:03.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.83,0:22:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.07,0:22:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't go away now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.35,0:22:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anybody there?
